reviewText: The original title was "The First of May."  Don't know why they changed this title!  It won several awards back in 1998 and was Dimaggio's last film.  Someone gave me this DVD and I haven't watched yet, but it gets very good reviews for a nice family film.
This is a film called "First of May" and is still available on Amazon.  What a cheap trick to re-release this film under another title. Booo.....
